{"id":945354919,"question_id":13,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 1 month","timestamp":1683357437,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/945354919/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"42.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int romanToInt(String s) {\n        int res = 0, n = s.length();\n        for(int i=0;i<n;i++){\n            char ch = s.charAt(i);\n            switch(ch){\n                case 'I':{\n                    if((i+1 < n) && (s.charAt(i+1) == 'V' || s.charAt(i+1) == 'X'))\n                        res-=1;\n                    else\n                        res+=1;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'V':{\n                    res+=5;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'X':{\n                    if((i+1 < n) && (s.charAt(i+1) == 'L' || s.charAt(i+1) == 'C'))\n                        res-=10;\n                    else\n                        res+=10;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'L':{\n                    res+=50;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'C':{\n                    if((i+1 < n) && (s.charAt(i+1) == 'D' || s.charAt(i+1) == 'M'))\n                        res-=100;\n                    else\n                        res+=100;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'D':{\n                    res+=500;\n                    break;\n                }\n                case 'M':{\n                    res+=1000;\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return res;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
